{
  "children": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "History of the Internet"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "The "
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Internet"
            }
          ],
          "type": "bold"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " is a global system of interconnected computer networks. Its origins trace back to research funded by the United States government in the 1960s"
        },
        {
          "label": "arpanet",
          "type": "footnote_ref"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "ARPANET"
        }
      ],
      "level": 2,
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "The Advanced Research Projects Agency Network (ARPANET) was the first wide-area packet-switched network"
        },
        {
          "keys": [
            {
              "key": "leiner2009"
            }
          ],
          "type": "citation"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": ". The first message was sent on October 29, 1969, from UCLA to Stanford"
        },
        {
          "keys": [
            {
              "key": "abbate2000"
            }
          ],
          "type": "citation"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "TCP/IP"
        }
      ],
      "level": 2,
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "The development of TCP/IP by Vint Cerf and Bob Kahn"
        },
        {
          "label": "tcpip",
          "type": "footnote_ref"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " in the 1970s provided a standardized protocol suite. This became the foundation of the modern Internet."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "The key innovation was packet switching, which allows multiple communication sessions to share a network simultaneously."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "World Wide Web"
        }
      ],
      "level": 2,
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Tim Berners-Lee invented the World Wide Web in 1989"
        },
        {
          "label": "bernerslee",
          "type": "footnote_ref"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " while working at CERN. The first website went live on August 6, 1991."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The web is more a social creation than a technical one. I designed it for a social effect -- to help people work together."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "type": "blockquote"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The distinction between the "
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "Internet"
                }
              ],
              "type": "italic"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " (network infrastructure) and the "
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "Web"
                }
              ],
              "type": "italic"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " (application layer) is often confused."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "foldable": false,
      "kind": "note",
      "type": "admonition"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Timeline"
        }
      ],
      "level": 2,
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "alignments": [
        "right",
        "none"
      ],
      "headers": [
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Year"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Event"
          }
        ]
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "1969"
            }
          ],
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "First ARPANET message sent"
            }
          ]
        ],
        [
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "1974"
            }
          ],
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "TCP/IP specification published"
            }
          ]
        ],
        [
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "1983"
            }
          ],
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "DNS introduced"
            }
          ]
        ],
        [
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "1989"
            }
          ],
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "World Wide Web proposed"
            }
          ]
        ],
        [
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "1991"
            }
          ],
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "First website goes live"
            }
          ]
        ],
        [
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "1993"
            }
          ],
          [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Mosaic browser released"
            }
          ]
        ]
      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The ARPANET was funded by the Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency (DARPA)."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "label": "arpanet",
      "type": "footnote_def"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Cerf, V. and Kahn, R. (1974). A Protocol for Packet Network Intercommunication."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "label": "tcpip",
      "type": "footnote_def"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Berners-Lee, T. (1989). Information Management: A Proposal."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "label": "bernerslee",
      "type": "footnote_def"
    }
  ]
}